page 4:
Drakan. A name that sends shivers down the spine od any sane man. We'd all heard the stories, The nightmares. Now, he has arrived at our doorstep.

The others aren't worried. 'The warriors will protect Hallowvale.' they say. They don't need to care. Their wives work in the city. They're safe but she is not.
